metadata.name: Symphonic Symbiotes #1
metadata.description: Symphonic Symbiotes celebrates the most perfect union of humanity and technology- the gift of music. These powerful and expressive beings reside in the spaces between your speakers and your eardrums, between the microphone and the voice, between the subwoofer and the beating heart. Through state of the art AI technology, we are able to catch glimpses of these spirits in all their majesty.
